o.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n酸口角唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n皮蛋個汁夠香 但唔夠酸 亦唔麻 唔掂 以10蚊黎講算抵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw我最憎澳門既餐廳就係唔會比紙巾 呢點真係討厭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b630e0e452df07085f40765ad663adac42b8e0b","tid":752780,"uid":23468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T06:11:26.000Z","msg":"咁平<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7be9d59ae1565d3bde01ac5fa0e563302e20bc98","tid":752780,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T08:38:05.000Z","msg":"開咗post了"},{"pid":"c824aef6df4de0fe248528d3550fea36abde5764","tid":752780,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b630e0e452df07085f40765ad663adac42b8e0b","tid":752780,"uid":23468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T06:11:26.000Z","msg":"咁平<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T09:41:34.000Z","msg":"正常價"}]}